{
  "text": "We have been speaking almost precisely of the portion of the Esmerelda Sweetwater book which we wrote having to do with Trostrick's misplacement of the space girl's mind/body/spirit complex. What is the significance of that work that we did with respect to our lives? It has been confusing to me for some time how that meshes in. Can you tell me that? I am Ra. We scan each and find we may speak.",
